Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.24,0:22:44.46,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}遗失了开启乐园的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.30,0:22:49.30,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}接受惩罚死去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.94,0:22:53.58,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}向着深夜的迷途
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.52,0:22:58.62,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}无法忍受的荆棘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.14,0:23:02.57,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}松开的锁链
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.74,0:23:12.26,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}追寻着永远被埋葬的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.03,0:23:21.85,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}请不要看这残破的我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.21,0:23:31.04,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}破裂的牵绊 黑色的安魂曲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.43,0:23:40.30,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}请不要来这里 这你未知的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.69,0:23:47.62,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}下着绝望的雨的世界……
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.67,0:23:49.07,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}现在、完结
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.25,0:23:54.72,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}如火焰般闪耀于汝等心中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.15,0:23:56.98,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}主宰汝等…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.24,0:22:44.46,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}楽園の扉開く　鍵を　失くして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.30,0:22:49.30,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}罰を受けし心は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.94,0:22:53.58,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}夜の迷路へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.52,0:22:58.62,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}茨の王　赦さず
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.14,0:23:02.57,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}解けめ鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.74,0:23:12.26,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}求めたのは　永遠　埋めたは愛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.03,0:23:21.85,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}穢れ壊れた　僕をみないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.21,0:23:31.04,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}裂かれた絆　黒きレクイエム
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.43,0:23:40.30,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}ここにこないで　君は知らないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.69,0:23:47.62,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}絶望の雨が降れる　世界が……
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.67,0:23:49.07,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}今、終わる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.25,0:23:54.72,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}Which Shinetu as a flame in the midst of your palace
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.15,0:23:56.98,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}And reigneth Amongst…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.03,0:01:03.04,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}月亮在轻轻低语
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.75,0:01:08.08,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}以谁也听不到的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.04,0:01:12.34,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur3}不断满涨的潮水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.30,0:01:16.30,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}消失渐远的记忆中的情景
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.72,0:01:22.06,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}星星在密密记述着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.39,0:01:26.77,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}以谁也无法解读的文字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.23,0:01:31.82,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}无限的语言的涡旋中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.11,0:01:36.53,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}千亿本书由此诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.53,0:01:44.00,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}我的天空无限广阔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.46,0:01:48.92,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}时间在飞速的镌刻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.09,0:01:54.59,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}毫无所知的虚无
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:01:58.01,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}汇聚的语言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.76,0:02:01.97,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}也只能在泥土中枯朽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.56,0:02:08.77,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}即使如此我仍在呼唤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.02,0:02:13.86,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}扬起晦涩难懂的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:19.07,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}至少将这声音传至天际
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.82,0:02:24.70,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}太阳也终会升起吧
